{"tid":1912931,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［經濟JJ］三個月內迎嚟第一波支爆","createTime":"2020-03-06T12:06:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T12:40:44.000Z","uid":21678,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ac7c1f89ef379f766d429200ebd0230912596ca6","tid":1912931,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:06:02.000Z","msg":"拋磚引玉<br />\n等其他高手指正<br />\n<br />\n武漢一月尾開始封城<br />\n二月全國休克<br />\n三月復工<br />\n<br />\n休克嘅呢一個月，幫助咗中國經濟製造咗一塊遮醜布<br />\n銀行可以用未全面復工為籍口<br />\n掩蓋債務違約問題<br />\n<br />\n中國民間債務<br />\n不嬲高得出奇<br />\n上至鐵路部果5萬億債項<br />\n下至打工仔人人孭二三百萬房貸<br />\n<br />\n一月新年前收完一期<br />\n二月遲交嘅款項，銀行可能以種種藉口推搪<br />\n例如因為企業未復工、債仔被隔離、債仔仲響鄕下...etc 去蒙混過去<br />\n<br />\n但係踏入三月<br />\n根據中央指示下<br />\n一切企業要恢復運作之下<br />\n意味住銀行業亦要重新投入運作<br />\n<br />\n即係話<br />\n債仔就須要一次過畀返二三月嘅錢<br />\n<br />\n以呢兩個月，中國嘅經濟狀況<br />\n就算有兩三成人國人手頭現金清倉<br />\n根本不足為奇<br />\n<br />\n換言之<br />\n去到四月初<br />\n第一波債務違約嘅統計數字就會爆出嚟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c5d1e27e56d77299e3878e9b9a9b05d165a42e","tid":1912931,"uid":21678,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:08:06.000Z","msg":"下一波<br />\n即係去到四月尾<br />\n收回欠款特別差嘅銀行<br />\n數據就會漸漸畀人揪出嚟<br />\n<br />\n而呢啲銀行嘅小存戶<br />\n就會爭相擠提"},{"pid":"a7006c58c9fa7f31dbe56d2c482681e9bc431891","tid":1912931,"uid":276908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:09:52.000Z","msg":"連國內銀行2月行既放水政策都未熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講經咩你"},{"pid":"594a318369bc65f18690142ee6eae942a2244aae","tid":1912931,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:13:01.000Z","msg":"咁你指教下你啲經呀"},{"pid":"9a5679237e0af2ca22584bf6677a9fe15011dcd3","tid":1912931,"uid":21678,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:13:59.000Z","msg":"好多人以為中共印銀紙係萬能嘅<br />\n事實相反<br />\n印銀紙去到某一點<br />\n人民對貨幣嘅信心崩潰<br />\n就會有反效果<br />\n變成人人搶外幣、搶貨物<br />\n都唔肯渣現金<br />\n<br />\n到時候中國就會變成委內瑞拉2.0<br />\n<br />\n要中共印銀紙幫銀行還錢嘅<br />\n發酵到大家唔再信任人仔<br />\n過程可以好快<br />\n甚至短到一個月、幾個星期、甚至十幾日<br />\n<br />\n換言之<br />\n最快去到五六月<br />\n就會出現第一波人民幣嘅信心危機"},{"pid":"1616f83039d4798d8e3b45cdb4b31caa6e715e37","tid":1912931,"uid":25240,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a7006c58c9fa7f31dbe56d2c482681e9bc431891","tid":1912931,"uid":276908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:09:52.000Z","msg":"連國內銀行2月行既放水政策都未熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講經咩你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:18:50.000Z","msg":"樓主識「教」班支那人武裝反抗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你估好似你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FmRBm4U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFmRBm4U.png&h=cce13da0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFYI<br />\n睇下11月廣東茂名點示威 （day1)<br />\n我已經唔貼呢排武肺班支那人點封路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/mouming-06_0zmns_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fmouming-06_0zmns_1200x0.png&h=78cd875d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲好笑過青頭仔教清水健點屌閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f9aa00d0c254ad073120b4bf14e95681f2fb8a","tid":1912931,"uid":21678,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a7006c58c9fa7f31dbe56d2c482681e9bc431891","tid":1912931,"uid":276908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:09:52.000Z","msg":"連國內銀行2月行既放水政策都未熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講經咩你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:19:58.000Z","msg":"如果你係講果1.2萬億放水<br />\n咁我可以答你<br />\n大陸銀行而家只會將流動性放畀國企同超大企業<br />\n新錢根本流唔到去人民果度<br />\n結果只有一個<br />\n就係大行冇事<br />\n但係中小企同房貸業主冚家剷<br />\n<br />\n咁請問銀行業點可能唔爆呢？"},{"pid":"fe1bbbb1c9b7094dd8c11ceee702b2114f42b072","tid":1912931,"uid":267937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:21:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e1db67c4bf1f5ab4225a2f7785df42be0c915c8","tid":1912931,"uid":136797,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:22:17.000Z","msg":"支爆講左幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本上呢一世都唔會發生"},{"pid":"4297e02e938b26873285777657e62cd17802e493","tid":1912931,"uid":11148,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:24:22.000Z","msg":"四月初,就睇下債務違約有冇爆 <br />\n<br />\n睇下智力97郭嘉既思考領域去到邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ad595c5dcfe2ef5ffbcfceb5cfc00d4550ef10","tid":1912931,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:24:25.000Z","msg":"支爆收成期<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cddf6ba4d9fe1a3288ff41d64b38b26bae7f0c71","tid":1912931,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4297e02e938b26873285777657e62cd17802e493","tid":1912931,"uid":11148,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:24:22.000Z","msg":"四月初,就睇下債務違約有冇爆 <br />\n<br />\n睇下智力97郭嘉既思考領域去到邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:25:18.000Z","msg":"「教」大陸人武裝起義算唔算勁？<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/FmRBm4U.png\" />"},{"pid":"70eccc0b88062018515118e4c3e959616fadbdf1","tid":1912931,"uid":21678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:28:04.000Z","msg":"中國債券違約響瘟疫來臨之前<br />\n就已經非常嚴重<br />\n銀行破產和擠兌響上年已經破哂紀錄<br />\n<br />\n企業虧損和倒閉，將帶來更大嘅違約風暴<br />\n然後拖垮更多的銀行破產<br />\n<br />\n已經對中共政權極度懷疑<br />\n喪失信心嘅人<br />\n一旦他們可以離開屋企<br />\n就會一窩蜂第一時間擠兌銀行<br />\n<br />\n當中共面臨幾千家、幾萬家銀行<br />\n同時現金耗盡嘅話<br />\n到時可能又要軍人維穩"},{"pid":"4e940c06dab18359c78f86998238b7963dfffb52","tid":1912931,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4297e02e938b26873285777657e62cd17802e493","tid":1912931,"uid":11148,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:24:22.000Z","msg":"四月初,就睇下債務違約有冇爆 <br />\n<br />\n睇下智力97郭嘉既思考領域去到邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:33:48.000Z","msg":"如果真係要檢視違約程度<br />\n唔單止要睇中國境內銀行<br />\n更重要嘅指標<br />\n就係香港銀行股<br />\n<br />\n因為香港有規有柜<br />\n監管之下冇咁易做假數<br />\n所以佢哋收唔返嘅大陸債項<br />\n先最反映到實際情況"},{"pid":"e176ff9d5d805ce2060a25de858030ccf5e0f812","tid":1912931,"uid":25240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e940c06dab18359c78f86998238b7963dfffb52","tid":1912931,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4297e02e938b26873285777657e62cd17802e493","tid":1912931,"uid":11148,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:24:22.000Z","msg":"四月初,就睇下債務違約有冇爆 <br />\n<br />\n睇下智力97郭嘉既思考領域去到邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:33:48.000Z","msg":"如果真係要檢視違約程度<br />\n唔單止要睇中國境內銀行<br />\n更重要嘅指標<br />\n就係香港銀行股<br />\n<br />\n因為香港有規有柜<br />\n監管之下冇咁易做假數<br />\n所以佢哋收唔返嘅大陸債項<br />\n先最反映到實際情況"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:36:40.000Z","msg":"認真一問 <br />\n樓主你悼念左個護旗手未？<br />\n<br />\n聽我講，我哋要集會悼念李文亮醫生！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1868534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1868534</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"63e2924696fbf15b24f895f069b626cbcc1f7353","tid":1912931,"uid":21678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:39:02.000Z","msg":"另一個更intuitive 嘅諗法<br />\n就係如果我係一個大陸打工仔<br />\n手頭嘅錢，可以頂到一兩個月開支<br />\n<br />\n由農曆年開始<br />\n差唔多去到三月尾<br />\n我嘅現金已經洗得七七八八<br />\n如果呢一刻還唔到錢<br />\n三月尾、四月頭已經會係咁畀銀行吹趨收久款<br />\n<br />\n如果收入再冇起基本上磨到六月<br />\n就一定要舉手老破"},{"pid":"579fb846010a0ed1b0d1414324dbbde3c1fef47c","tid":1912931,"uid":63779,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T14:04:02.000Z","msg":"算吧啦，無戰爭既情況下支那根本唔會爆，要爆廿年前一早爆左，本身支那就算係資源豐富，支那華人連港豬iq算係平均比較高，地廣而可用地多，人亦都多，80-90年代俾佢選左條賣奴隸既路，港豬同支那豬日本人都係完美既員工，所以政府玩血汗工廠之後，支那係蒸蒸日上，尤其港豬幫手俾資金同技術，到2000年，基本上外資都係支那設廠，就算佢地走晒d廠，但技術都走唔到，支那照樣可以賣野俾第三國家而無視版權，最重要既野全世界既投行都係買支那既股票，而支那既券商又買返外資，基本上係密不可分既關係，睇清現實啦，根本就全世界少數人幫手奴役緊中產同窮人，支那興起只不過多左班有錢人同一大班高增值奴隸姐。"},{"pid":"a5e40f304cb8084ceccd47b8406014b346e20745","tid":1912931,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:43:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81df3a6b010ae7ae3e3b65b395e5d4d8ff0e810","tid":1912931,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1616f83039d4798d8e3b45cdb4b31caa6e715e37","tid":1912931,"uid":25240,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a7006c58c9fa7f31dbe56d2c482681e9bc431891","tid":1912931,"uid":276908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:09:52.000Z","msg":"連國內銀行2月行既放水政策都未熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講經咩你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:18:50.000Z","msg":"樓主識「教」班支那人武裝反抗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你估好似你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<